## ğŸ“š Overview

Veritus is a legal AI assistant designed for accuracy, transparency, and jurisdiction-specific insight. Built to assist lawyers, students, and legal researchers, Veritus delivers citation-backed legal information without hallucinations. 

Its hybrid architecture combines retrieval-augmented generation (RAG), structured legal databases, and a luxury-grade frontend experience â€” all to provide AI thatâ€™s not only smart, but reliable and trustworthy.

